@required {resourceArn: str, tags: [Tag]}

@endpoint POST /
@desc Remove a customer tag from a resource. A tag is a key-value pair of metadata associated with an Proton resource. For more information, see Proton resources and tagging in the Proton User Guide.
@required {resourceArn: str, tagKeys: [str]}

@endpoint POST /
@desc Update Proton settings that are used for multiple services in the Amazon Web Services account.
